dct_description_sm: City map includes paragraph with geographic description and information for purchasing lots. Also six lithograph drawings of specific buildings in Brielle. A small map of Northeastern US railroads is in lower right corner.
Robert A. Weicke, Photo-Lithographer, 178 William St., New York NY
